        'English' => 'What personal data do we collect about you?<br><br>We collect personal data from you when you provide it to us directly and through your use of the Site. This information may include:<br><br>• Information you provide to us when you use our Site (e.g. your name, contact details, product reviews, and any information which you add our site);<br><br>• Transaction and billing information, if you make any purchases from us or using our Site (e.g. PayPal details and delivery information);<br><br>• Records of your interactions with us (e.g. if you contact our customer service team, interact with us on social media);<br><br>• Information you provide us when you enter a competition or participate in a survey;<br><br>• Information collected automatically, using cookies and other tracking technologies .<br><br>What do we use this personal data for?<br><br>Depending on how you use our Site, your interactions with us, and the permissions you give us, the purposes for which we use your personal data include:<br><br>• To fulfill your order<br><br>• To manage and respond to any queries or complaints to our customer service team.<br><br>• To improve and maintain the Site, and monitor its usage.<br><br>• For market research, e.g. we may contact you for feedback about our products.<br><br>• For security purposes, to investigate fraud and where necessary to protect ourselves and third parties.<br><br>• To comply with our legal and regulatory obligations.<br><br>We rely on the following legal basis, under data protection law, to process your personal data:<br><br>• Because the processing is necessary to perform a contract with you, or take steps prior to entering into a contract with you (e.g. where you have made a purchase with us, we use your personal data to process the payment and fulfill your order).<br><br>• Because it is in our legitimate interests as an e-commerce provider to maintain and promote our services. We are always seeking to understand more about our customers in order to offer the best products and customer experience.<br><br>Who do we share this personal data with?<br><br>We may share information with governmental agencies or other companies assisting us in fraud prevention or investigation. We may do so when:<br><br>• Permitted or required by law; or,<br><br>• Trying to protect against or prevent actual or potential fraud or unauthorized transactions; or,<br><br>• Investigating fraud which has already taken place. The information is not provided to these companies for marketing purposes.<br><br>We may also disclose your personal information, without notice, if such action is necessary to:<br><br>• Conform to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on the Site;<br><br>• Protect and defend the rights or property of the Site;<br><br>• Act in urgent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of the Site.<br><br>Security<br><br>This Site ensures that data is encrypted when leaving the Site. This process involves the converting of information or data into a code to prevent unauthorized access. This Site follows this process and employs secure methods to ensure the protection of all payment transactions. Encryption methods such as SSL are utilized to protect customer data when in transit to and from this Site over a secure communications channel.<br><br>Whilst we do everything within our power to ensure that personal data is protected at all times from our Site, we cannot guarantee the security and integrity of the information that has been transmitted to our Site.<br><br>Cookies<br><br>The Site may use cookie and tracking technology depending on the features offered. Cookie and tracking technology are useful for gathering information such as browser type and operating system, tracking the number of visitors to the Site, and understanding how visitors use the Site. Cookies can also help customize the Site for visitors. Personal information cannot be collected via cookies and other tracking technology, however, if you previously provided personally identifiable information, cookies may be tied to such information. Aggregate cookie and tracking information may be shared with third parties.<br><br>Contact Us<br><br>If you have any questions, concerns, or comments about our privacy policy you may contact us.',
        'Chinese-fan' => 'ydzshop&nbsp;隱私聲明 <br> 我們十分重視客戶的隱私。因此, 我們只會根據本隱私聲明擬 定之方式收集及使用您的個人資料。<br> 1) 在有必要或與交易有關時向您收集資料。<br> 2) 在法例要求或與收集用途有關時才會保留您的資料。<br> 您可以在不提供個人資料的情況下瀏覽ydzshop網站。在沒有登入用戶帳號瀏覽我們的網站時, 您將會以匿名身份瀏覽, 而我們無法辦出您的身份。<br> 我們十分樂意聆聽您的意見。若您有任何意見或建議, 請將有關資料電郵至&nbsp; <a href="mailto:hyfhdcjn@gmail.com" style="color:#F8770E">hyfhdcjn@gmail.com</a><br> 個人資料收集<br> ydzshop不會向第三方出售、分享或買賣網上收集的客戶個人資料。網上收集的個人資料僅於本公司集團內披露以供內部使用。建立ydzshop帳戶時, 我們將向您收集的基本個人資料包含:<br> 1) 姓名<br> 2) 送貨地址<br> 3) 電郵地址<br> 4) 聯絡電話號碼<br> 5) 出生日期<br> 6) 性別<br> 我們所向您收集的個人資料將會作為以下用途:<br> 1) 運送您在ydzshop所購買的商品<br> 2) 提供商品運送狀況和客戶支援的最新消息<br> 3) 為您提供有關商品的資料<br> 4) 處理您的訂單, 或根據您的要求或透過我們網站提供服務和資訊<br> 此外, 我們也會使用您所提供的資料管理您的帳戶; 驗證及進行您的網上付款有關交易; 審查從我們網站下載的資料; 辨識網站瀏覽器; 做網站用戶統計進行調查; 在您表明不拒絕接收訊息的情況下, 發送我們認為適合您的相關商品或服務資訊。<br> 我們可能會將您的姓名和地址交給第三者 (例如速遞公司或供應商), 以方便送貨。<br> 注：速遞公司有權要求您填寫身份證號碼，爲了提供海關內部查閱和核對以方便安排出口。<br> 我們可能會保留您的訂單資料, 但基於保安理由, 我們不能直接檢索該資料。您可以登入帳戶, 存取訂單資料, 查詢個人訂單資料。您也可以管理個人地址、銀行資料和已訂閱的電子報。您有責任確保個人資料保密, 並不會讓未授權的第三方得到這些資料。我們不會承擔任何不當使用密碼的責任。<br> 個人資料安全<br> ydzshop確保會安全和保密地保存所有收集到的資料。我們會以下列方式保護您的個人資料:<br> 1) 限制存取個人資料<br> 2) 維護科技產品防止未經授權存取電腦資料<br> 3) 當資料沒有保留作記綠的用途, 我們會在安全情況下銷毀您的個人資料<br> ydzshop使用128位元安全通訊端層保密技術 (SSL) 處理您的財務資料。128位元安全通訊端層保密技術大約需要至少一萬億年破解, 並且為業界標準的安全措施。<br> 個人資料披露<br> 除了提供ydzshop網站送貨服務的相關公司及相關第三方以外, 我們不會將您的個人資料分享給其他機構。<br> 在特殊情況下,&nbsp;ydzshop可能會被要求披露個人資料, 例如: 在有理由相信的情況下披露個人資料有助阻止生命或健康受到威脅, 或作執法用途。<br> 如果你認為ydzshop違反了隱私條例, 請發電郵至 <a href="mailto:hyfhdcjn@gmail.com" style="color:#F8770E">hyfhdcjn@gmail.com</a><br> 電腦數據收集<br> 當您瀏覽ydzshop網站時, 本公司的伺服器會自動記錄您的瀏覽器所傳送的資料。資料包括:<br> - 您的電腦IP地址<br> - 瀏覽器類別<br> - 瀏覽我們網站前所瀏覽的網頁<br> - 在ydzshop網站內瀏覽的頁面<br> - 於上述頁面的使用時間、於我們網站搜尋的產品及資料、存取時間及日期, 以及其他統計數據。<br> 收集所得的資料會用作分析和評估, 從而幫助改善本網站及我們提供的服務和產品。這些資料不會與其他個人資料一同使用。<br> 隱私聲明更改<br> ydzshop保留隨時修改和更改隱私聲明的權利。<br> 有關違反隱私條例的投訴<br> 如果對我們處理客戶隱私或投訴的方法有任何不滿, 請發電郵至 <a href="mailto:hyfhdcjn@gmail.com" style="color:#F8770E">hyfhdcjn@gmail.com</a>聯絡我們。',
        'Indonesia' => 'Data pribadi apa yang kami kumpulkan tentang Anda?<br><br>Kami mengumpulkan data pribadi dari Anda ketika Anda memberikannya kepada kami secara langsung dan melalui penggunaan Situs oleh Anda. Informasi ini dapat meliputi:<br><br>• Informasi yang Anda berikan kepada kami ketika Anda menggunakan Situs kami (mis. Nama Anda, detail kontak, ulasan produk, dan informasi apa pun yang Anda tambahkan di situs kami);<br><br>• Informasi transaksi dan penagihan, jika Anda melakukan pembelian dari kami atau menggunakan Situs kami (mis. Detail PayPal dan informasi pengiriman);<br><br>• Catatan interaksi Anda dengan kami (misalnya. Jika Anda menghubungi tim layanan pelanggan kami, berinteraksi dengan kami di media sosial);<br><br>• Informasi yang Anda berikan kepada kami ketika Anda mengikuti kompetisi atau berpartisipasi dalam survei;<br><br>• Informasi dikumpulkan secara otomatis, menggunakan cookie dan teknologi pelacakan lainnya.<br><br>Kami akan menggunakan data pribadi ini untuk apa ?<br><br>Bergantung pada bagaimana Anda menggunakan Situs kami, interaksi Anda dengan kami, dan izin yang Anda berikan kepada kami, tujuan kami menggunakan data pribadi Anda meliputi:<br><br>• Untuk memenuhi pesanan Anda<br><br>• Untuk mengelola dan menanggapi pertanyaan atau keluhan apa pun kepada tim layanan pelanggan kami.<br><br>• Untuk meningkatkan dan memelihara Situs, dan memantau penggunaannya.<br><br>• Untuk riset pasar, mis. kami dapat menghubungi Anda untuk umpan balik tentang produk kami.<br><br>• Untuk tujuan keamanan, untuk menyelidiki penipuan dan jika perlu untuk melindungi diri kita sendiri dan pihak ketiga.<br><br>• Untuk mematuhi kewajiban hukum dan peraturan kami.<br><br>Kami mengandalkan dasar hukum berikut, di bawah undang-undang perlindungan data, untuk memproses data pribadi Anda:<br><br>• Karena pemrosesan diperlukan untuk melakukan kontrak dengan Anda, atau mengambil langkah-langkah sebelum menandatangani kontrak dengan Anda (misalnya. Tempat  Anda melakukan pembelian dengan kami, kami menggunakan data pribadi Anda untuk memproses pembayaran dan memenuhi pesanan Anda).<br><br>• Karena kepentingan kami yang sah sebagai penyedia e-commerce untuk mempertahankan dan mempromosikan layanan kami. Kami selalu berusaha memahami lebih banyak tentang pelanggan kami untuk menawarkan produk dan pengalaman pelanggan terbaik.<br><br>Dengan siapa kami berbagi data pribadi ini?<br><br>Kami dapat berbagi informasi dengan lembaga pemerintah atau perusahaan lain yang membantu kami dalam pencegahan atau penyelidikan penipuan. Kami dapat melakukannya ketika:<br><br>• Diijinkan atau diharuskan oleh hukum; atau,<br><br>• Berusaha melindungi atau mencegah penipuan aktual atau potensial atau transaksi tidak sah; atau,<br><br>• Investigasi penipuan yang sudah terjadi. Informasi tidak diberikan kepada perusahaan-perusahaan ini untuk tujuan pemasaran.<br><br>Kami juga dapat mengungkapkan informasi pribadi Anda, tanpa pemberitahuan, jika tindakan tersebut diperlukan untuk:<br><br>• Mematuhi ketentuan hukum atau mematuhi proses hukum yang disajikan di Situs;<br><br>• Melindungi dan mempertahankan hak atau properti Situs;<br><br>• Bertindak dalam keadaan mendesak untuk melindungi keamanan pribadi pengguna Situs.<br><br>Keamanan<br><br>Situs ini memastikan bahwa data dienkripsi ketika meninggalkan Situs. Proses ini melibatkan konversi informasi atau data menjadi kode untuk mencegah akses yang tidak sah. Situs ini mengikuti proses ini dan menggunakan metode aman untuk memastikan perlindungan semua transaksi pembayaran. Metode enkripsi seperti SSL digunakan untuk melindungi data pelanggan saat dalam perjalanan ke dan dari Situs ini melalui saluran komunikasi yang aman.<br><br>Sementara kami melakukan segala daya kami untuk memastikan bahwa data pribadi dilindungi setiap saat dari Situs kami, kami tidak dapat menjamin keamanan dan integritas informasi yang telah dikirim ke Situs kami.<br><br>Cookie<br><br>Situs dapat menggunakan cookie dan teknologi pelacakan tergantung pada fitur yang ditawarkan. Teknologi cookie dan pelacakan berguna untuk mengumpulkan informasi seperti jenis browser dan sistem operasi, melacak jumlah pengunjung ke Situs, dan memahami bagaimana pengunjung menggunakan Situs. Cookie juga dapat membantu menyesuaikan Situs untuk pengunjung. Informasi pribadi tidak dapat dikumpulkan melalui cookie dan teknologi pelacakan lainnya, namun, jika sebelumnya Anda memberikan informasi pengenal pribadi, cookie dapat dikaitkan dengan informasi tersebut. Cookie gabungan dan informasi pelacakan dapat dibagi dengan pihak ketiga.<br><br>Hubungi kami<br><br>Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, masalah, atau komentar tentang kebijakan privasi kami, Anda dapat menghubungi kami.',
        'Arab' => 'What personal data do we collect about you?<br><br>We collect personal data from you when you provide it to us directly and through your use of the Site. This information may include:<br><br>• Information you provide to us when you use our Site (e.g. your name, contact details, product reviews, and any information which you add our site);<br><br>• Transaction and billing information, if you make any purchases from us or using our Site (e.g. PayPal details and delivery information);<br><br>• Records of your interactions with us (e.g. if you contact our customer service team, interact with us on social media);<br><br>• Information you provide us when you enter a competition or participate in a survey;<br><br>• Information collected automatically, using cookies and other tracking technologies .<br><br>What do we use this personal data for?<br><br>Depending on how you use our Site, your interactions with us, and the permissions you give us, the purposes for which we use your personal data include:<br><br>• To fulfill your order<br><br>• To manage and respond to any queries or complaints to our customer service team.<br><br>• To improve and maintain the Site, and monitor its usage.<br><br>• For market research, e.g. we may contact you for feedback about our products.<br><br>• For security purposes, to investigate fraud and where necessary to protect ourselves and third parties.<br><br>• To comply with our legal and regulatory obligations.<br><br>We rely on the following legal basis, under data protection law, to process your personal data:<br><br>• Because the processing is necessary to perform a contract with you, or take steps prior to entering into a contract with you (e.g. where you have made a purchase with us, we use your personal data to process the payment and fulfill your order).<br><br>• Because it is in our legitimate interests as an e-commerce provider to maintain and promote our services. We are always seeking to understand more about our customers in order to offer the best products and customer experience.<br><br>Who do we share this personal data with?<br><br>We may share information with governmental agencies or other companies assisting us in fraud prevention or investigation. We may do so when:<br><br>• Permitted or required by law; or,<br><br>• Trying to protect against or prevent actual or potential fraud or unauthorized transactions; or,<br><br>• Investigating fraud which has already taken place. The information is not provided to these companies for marketing purposes.<br><br>We may also disclose your personal information, without notice, if such action is necessary to:<br><br>• Conform to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on the Site;<br><br>• Protect and defend the rights or property of the Site;<br><br>• Act in urgent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of the Site.<br><br>Security<br><br>This Site ensures that data is encrypted when leaving the Site. This process involves the converting of information or data into a code to prevent unauthorized access. This Site follows this process and employs secure methods to ensure the protection of all payment transactions. Encryption methods such as SSL are utilized to protect customer data when in transit to and from this Site over a secure communications channel.<br><br>Whilst we do everything within our power to ensure that personal data is protected at all times from our Site, we cannot guarantee the security and integrity of the information that has been transmitted to our Site.<br><br>Cookies<br><br>The Site may use cookie and tracking technology depending on the features offered. Cookie and tracking technology are useful for gathering information such as browser type and operating system, tracking the number of visitors to the Site, and understanding how visitors use the Site. Cookies can also help customize the Site for visitors. Personal information cannot be collected via cookies and other tracking technology, however, if you previously provided personally identifiable information, cookies may be tied to such information. Aggregate cookie and tracking information may be shared with third parties.<br><br>Contact Us<br><br>If you have any questions, concerns, or comments about our privacy policy you may contact us.',
